well its been a while seens the last time i wrote here :-/ i think it was aout the car accident,i just dont know what to write,like today jeje,so let talk about what ive been doing and all that..

i've been hanging out with Yans(high school friend),Damaso(college best friend and some other friends from college...but most of the time its yans,damaso and me jeje...mm we've gone to san juan...took lots of picture :P went to el condado,to a little plaza with a bar and the beach right next to it,its a really nice place i love going there :P mostly because of the beach jej,mm went to dorado,not only to pick damaso up but eat chinese food and go to the beach jeje really fun..most of the times is the same things so jeje oh and last thursday we went to starbucks first then to The Embassy with Manota,Gabriel,Luis(a.k.a blaze),jonathan.. only that luis and gaby didnt go with us to the embassy...they suck i know lol... anyway its was fun,although some strange things happened there jejeje ;) u know what im talking about and who lol so anyway jk,although its true some weird things happened and most of the time i was thinking :-/ nothing new lol but anyway it was fun hope we do it again :P...maybe tomorrow we are hanging out again... let see

mm yans leaving on the 28 of this month.. sucks cause now its when we started hanging out,i didnt saw or talk to her seens 9th grade so yea..sucks... hopefully she comes to visit and then we can all hangout,and maybe my mom wont start fighting about the time and when im coming home jeje... but i understand her :)...mm anyway yea, shes leaving.. now im going to be alone with all this crazy guys :-/ *eekk* jeje anyway that about it...♥peace!im out!♥ :)

Yesterday,well today at 1:20am,my bro got home from NY.i called us at 1:25am.. so we get ready,and go in my car.. we took the same route we always take..cogemos,i dont know the name of that street,then we go to the right y vamos para la calle de la universidad la UPR,ahi hay una luz..so bajamos la velocidad,para chekear si venia carro,esta verde para nosotras, pero si venia una guagua, q paso? esa guagua iba super rapido probably like 40mph kinda of,ella no bajo la velocidad ni esquivo ni nada,so no choco en el lado de el pasajero,el lado donde yo estaba,me choco,mi guagua se viro y ademas de eso dio una vuelta hasta llegar a un murito q estaba en el otro lado de la calle, enverdad no sabemos muy bn cm paso,cm quedamo mirando hacia el lado en q veniamos,mami estaba like pega en el la puerta de ella y yo cm si fuera flying de lado :-/,nos desamaramos,we tried to get out of the car BUT ninguna de las puerta abrian so i got a panic attack pq ademas de eso,de el accidente tambn vi un humito so lo primero q me vino a la mente fue.. q el carro iba a explortar,dramatic maybe ut i got freaked out...so yeah got panic attack but then came like 5 police cars out of nowhere,and my mom gave them the car keys por la ventana del lado q nos choco la muchacha ya q se habia salido de sitio,el polica abrio la puerta del baul(sp?) y pudimos salir...i got so freaked out q no sabia q hacer all i asked was my mom..where is she?is she ok??,they asked me if i had someone that i can called and i said i needed to call my bro bcause we where on our way to pick him up in the airport so i gave them the number and they talked to him telling him that we were in an accidente but we were ok then she passed me the phone so i can talked to him,i told everything but then i passed the phone to mom so she explain where were we,he took a taxi from the airport(which is weird cause therent many taxis on that airport anyway he took the taxi and got to the placed and looked for us,we were on the ambulance,they were cheking if we were alright then he he went to get moms car to takes us home,thenn my dad came all the way from Caguas to see if we were alright and to see if nothing really serou happened and to see my car and see what we were going to do with it...funny thing is,kind of, was that my car was only scratched up and sort of bent where she hits us,el retrovisor del conductor fucked up pero ningun cristal se rompio ni la puerta se undio mucho... y con el cantaso q ella nos dio era para  saliera la puerta por el otro lado :-/..

anyway thank god we are ok,just bruises..mami en el seno derecho, probabky from the seat belt or stering wheel and me,mi hombro hurts y part del pecho probably tambn del cinturon,cm nos dio super duro ps el cinturon nos aguanto tan duro q ps nos lastimo,manana ps voy a ir con mami a hacerme unos examenes just to make sure q no tengamos nada serio and yeah well manana voy a la uni,so i see you guys there,hopefully in better shape than today and well not in so much pain :-/

 that's the sad story... and well to anyone who reads this PLEASE nose coman la luces,dont drink and drive or use drugs for that matter.. becuase this is what happenes..accidentes q nadie puede evitar,solo tu los puedes evitar no hacieno esas cosas...mm nose q mas decirte, mm estoy mas tranquila,no estoy tann nerviosa pero si me paso llorando like everytime i think of that. mm anyway g2g take care and love ya guys :)

anyway...update...

been doing the same thing every day jeje...shooping,walking in the mall alone,taking my mom to her job,stay at home listening to music,watching tv balh blah blah jeje same old same old except ive been going alot to starbucks,i love starbucks! lol i think they already know us, they even remember my moms name lol so cool,and they are really nice too..cool ppl..

i havent done any earring or bracelets seens no one want to buy real things,apparently adult ppl prefer fake stuff lol.. oh well,anyway now what im doing is cellphone thingies,not what they are called lol,anyway those thingies that you put on your cel,mmm cadenita,no se cm se le dice :-/ anywayyy ps eso estoy haciendo ahora, and they are cooolll :P.. i havent sold any of the coral,turquoise bracelets...ppl they are really coral and turquoise ok! i cant sell them at 5 bucks when they cost me like 10 buck a string of only 10-15 rocks!! sorry but i cant...anyway :D everything cool jeje.. yeah that the update of my jewelry jeje
